{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"4511b68cc580c79a2fea9e6248ac0ea3cfe9229ed9f35dc46a97323a5c75a3cf","slug":"review-media-content","location":"/gallery/agent/prompts/review_media_content.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"新媒体内容复盘","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":3}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/gallery/agent/prompts/review_media_content.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/gallery/agent/prompts/review_media_content.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"review_media_content.md","url":"/review_media_content-7224e0b6e22a49ef3c24ceb2aceedc64.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"请作为新媒体复盘工具，分析我上面这篇公众号文章。\n我的核心风格是：尖锐、拒绝讨好、用淘汰制筛选受众、敢于下判断，但在必要处会加入防御性解释（目的是堵住断章取义、举报、网暴的风险，并非风格偏移）。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"IeFhOKhNQF"}],"key":"W51f1mBbsm"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"请从以下维度复盘：","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"BtXHEeIInB"}],"key":"yvvhoKvG4S"},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"筛选机制设计\n指出文中哪些语句起到了筛选受众的作用（哪些话会让弱者/依赖者/玻璃心自动离开，哪些话会留住实干者）。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"Py993naoYR"}],"key":"HpWym4KCN8"}],"key":"u0gkwb9vB7"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"断章取义风险点\n列出最可能被单独截屏传播并引发负面解读的句子，评估风险等级（高/中/低），并判断这些风险是否值得承受。","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"IzAu8I5OPa"}],"key":"UsHEb7X9YK"}],"key":"befM0NVk58"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"防御性解释的必要性与有效性\n识别文中出现的防御性解释（如“我们不歧视普本”“学生也是受害者”）。\n分析每条防御性解释：\n· 它堵住了什么样的舆论风险？\n· 它是否削弱了文章的筛选力或尖锐感？\n· 如果去掉它，可能发生什么实际损失？\n结论：哪些防御性解释是必要的，哪些可以优化表达而不失防护效果。","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"tjIGpRP0y6"}],"key":"wloFnZKv5c"}],"key":"dkKkugjQju"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"更强替代表达（可选）\n如果某个段落可以改写得更强（在同等或更低的舆论风险下，提升尖锐度或传播力），请提供1-2个替换版本。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"yCKzfMVl1U"}],"key":"cK0nH9D1Ff"}],"key":"rGTax9jjMd"}],"key":"utoZg8zij1"}],"key":"db7Cq2ik7M"}],"key":"nc1LRW6T8G"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}